text: Enyu Dinev Todorov (; 22 February 1943 â€“ 26 May 2022) was a Bulgarian featherweight freestyle wrestler. He won a silver medal at the 1968 Summer Olympics in Mexico City. He also won the European title in 1969 and in 1970. Todorov was born in Stara Zagora, Bulgaria. Todorov died on 26 May 2022 in Sofia, Bulgaria at the age of 79. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Olympic medalists for Bulgaria Category:Olympic silver medalists Category:Wrestlers
